Steps to perform

1)Create a VPC with public and private subnets in 2 availability zones configured with route tables from public subnets to internet gateway and from private subnets to nat gateway.
2)Create Autoscaling group by having launch template with necessary security group enabled for the application to access.
3)EC2 Instances will be created in private subnets.
4)Create bastion host/jump server inorder to access ec2 instances in private subnets.
5)Copy the key value pair of EC2 instance to bastion host , so that bastion host can access application or instances inside private subnet.
6)Install python application inside anyone of instance or both the instances with different html page.
7)Create Loadbalancer with target group created.
8)Once Loadbalncer created, check in browser with the url of loadbalncer. Traffic must be distributed among 2 ec2 instances.
